## Dependencies

### Internal Dependencies
- Existing Telegram bot infrastructure (`server/telegram.ts`)
- Database schema stability (users, collaborations, requests tables)
- Admin permission system
- Notification preference system

### External Dependencies
- Telegram Bot API availability and stability
- Database connection reliability
- Server infrastructure capacity

### Team Dependencies
- Backend engineer for core implementation
- Product manager for admin user training
